<A>__{the boy just waits, sad, lonely. the teacher offers lhamo an apricot. lhamo takes the fruit. the monk pats the boy's head, gently, and lhamo takes shelter in the kind man's massive robes. the view becomes sunlight through deep, maroon wool.}
